page.title: 19Ladock Woods 1.
page.content: We went to Ladock Woods and we saw lots of trees. We saw a nest with about five hundred ants in it. Malcolm found another nest that had so many that it looked black. John found a massive fir cone and we found many cones on the ground. I found the hole of a mouse or a shrew. Then we went deeper into the wood. These are the creatures we found: { Woodlice Frog Hoppers { Worms Spiders { Ants Snails { Slugs Greenfly { Beetles We saw many plants, trees and grasses in the woods. Here are some of them: { Rhododendron Leyland Cypress { Mountain Sorrel Norway Spruce { Elder Japanese Larch { Lime-stone Monterey Pine { Fir cones Douglas Fir
